---
title: Agent Handoff Sequence
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant D as Studio Director
    participant SR as Source Researcher
    participant PA as presentation-architect
    participant VD as visual-designer
    participant IG as infographic-designer
    participant DV as data-storyteller
    participant AN as animation-director
    participant AR as academic-reviewer
    participant EX as Builder + Exporter

    User->>D: request + sources + target formats
    D->>SR: ingest sources
    SR-->>D: evidence_ledger.json
    D->>PA: brief + ledger
    PA-->>D: outline.json (story structure)
    D->>User: ⛔ approve outline (ghost-deck)?
    User-->>D: approved
    par Produce (parallel)
        D->>VD: outline + brand
        VD-->>D: theme.json + layouts
        D->>IG: structural slides
        IG-->>D: diagram exhibits
        D->>DV: data slides
        DV-->>D: chart/table exhibits
        D->>AN: deck elements + delivery mode
        AN-->>D: animation plan
    end
    D->>EX: deck_spec + theme + assets
    EX-->>D: deck.pptx / html / revealjs / frontend
    D->>AR: deck_spec + ledger + rendered deck
    AR-->>D: review_report (pass/fail, veto)
    alt fail
        AR->>D: route fix to responsible agent
    else pass
        D->>User: PPTX · PDF · HTML · RevealJS · Frontend
    end
